window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Leonora Romilly was murdered. The catch? She didn't stay dead.</p> <p>Instead, she finds herself alive-ish and swept away to Ashvale to learn how to be a fully-functioning, albeit undead, member of society.</p> <p>At Ashvale, the blood runs free and the sexual tension never sleeps, but under the surface, something much more sinister lurks.</p> <p>With her would-be murderer still roaming free, a new-found love, and her lost memories on the line, can Leonora survive Ashvale with both her head and her heart intact?</p>"; 
